### Talus Tally API Testing
### Use VS Code REST Client extension
### Workflow: 1) Health Check 2) Create Project 3) Copy session_id below 4) Try other requests

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1
@session_id = 
@root_node_id = 

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### List Templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates

###

### Get Template Schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates/restomod/schema

###

### 1. CREATE NEW PROJECT FIRST - Copy session_id and root id from response
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template_id": "restomod",
  "project_name": "My Test Project"
}

###

### 2. AFTER creating project, paste session_id into @session_id variable above
### Then uncomment and use the requests below:

### Get Project Tree
# GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{session_id}}/graph/tree

###

### Execute Command - Create Node
# POST {{baseUrl}}/commands/execute
# Content-Type: application/json
# 
# {
#   "session_id": "{{session_id}}",
#   "command_type": "CreateNode",
#   "data": {
#     "parent_id": "{{root_node_id}}",
#     "blueprint_type_id": "task",
#     "name": "New Task"
#   }
# }

###

### Undo Last Command
# POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{session_id}}/undo

###

### Redo Last Command
# POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{session_id}}/redo

